CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: DiaMedica Therapeutics Inc is a clinical-stage biopharmaceutical company. The company is principally engaged in the business activity of developing treatments for unmet clinical needs or where no therapies are available with a primary focus on chronic kidney disease and acute ischemicstroke. Its pipeline product DM199 is a recombinant form of human tissue kallikrein-1.
